combine
 - 135 g flour
 - 2 tsp baking powder
whisk together in a bowl
 - 1 egg
 - 45 g oil
whisk in
 - 2 tsp sugar
 - 1/8 tsp salt
 - 1 tsp vanilla extract
 - 200 g milk
whisk in flour mix
rest 1 hour

yelds 2.5 scrapped 3/4 cup servings
use 1 cup batter for denser results ( Julien )

set iron to 200C
brush iron with oil just before every cook
cook for 2.5 minutes for 3/4 cup
cook for 3 minutes for 1 cup


reheat from room temperature in 200C iron for 45 seconds

